title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 15 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 15 2022
description:
Dr. Marty Makary of Johns Hopkins with the covid latest and the answer to the question, "Can men get pregnant?" Will the plot of the movie Juwanna Mann come true, with males playing female professional sports? Rep. Mayra Flores joins Clay and Buck to talk about her mission to save America as we know it. Former Congressman and the CEO of TRUTH Social, Devin Nunes, talks with C&B about the demise of the Musk Twitter deal and the growth of TRUTH Social.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
